name: Javad Doliskani
content: Jake Doliskani Jake Doliskani Home Research Contact Positions ☰ Home Research Contact Positions I am an Assistant Professor at the Department of Computing and Software at McMaster University. Before coming to McMaster, I was a faculty member at TMU, and before that, I was an NSERC post-doctoral fellow at the Institute for Quantum Computing at the University of Waterloo. I did my PhD in Computer Science with Éric Schost at the Ontario Research Center for Computer Algebra. I am interested in Post-Quantum Cryptography, Quantum Computing, and Applied Cryptography.
